- Medipol \'dcniversitesi Hastanesi\'97 G\'f6r\'fc\uc0\u351 \'fcyoruz, cuma g\'fcn\'fc tekrar telefonda g\'f6r\'fc\u351 t\'fck. Klinik ara\u351 t\u305 rma i\'e7in s\u305 cak bak\u305 yorlar, haftaya tekrar y\'fczy\'fcze g\'f6r\'fc\u351 ece\u287 iz. \
